[size=2][b][anchor=introduction]1.0 - Introduction[/b][/size]

Hello! This is a quest designed to make you know more about quests! It's named, "Here We Go Again!" Here We Go Again!, I will show you the quest description, like how it does in RS Wiki:

“You are hired by the Fear Reaper and Sir Prysin to take down someone, or something!

Help him and prove you are the greatest and strongest Warrior in the world!”

<blockquote>[img]http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-H4I2_Hv0zS8/TrsRstCpL7I/AAAAAAAAC_0/q86MqylaSq4/s1600/quick+tip.jpg[/img]

It's nice to add this to the quest interface.</blockquote>

